{"tid":1884323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【2BoxesThx!】估你唔到, 連口罩都可以整到地圖網 ?","createTime":"2020-02-17T13:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:09:17.000Z","uid":69134,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4bdb822ae68dea4260b537c4b383acd429a4b0","tid":1884323,"uid":69134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"我朋友呢幾日得閒得濟整左個地圖網出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.2boxesthx.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.2boxesthx.com%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=5e0e75af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.2boxesthx.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUbGFET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUbGFET.png&h=38412f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJoRirz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJoRirz.png&h=c2e43815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2BoxesThx呢個網其實係個物資分享/求助平台 (包括但不限於口罩)<br />\n目標係想將現時短缺的各種資源分配比D好有需要的人。<br />\n每人分享既資源唔一定要好多，盡量係唔影響自己的情況下分享幾個口罩就可以。<br />\n所謂聚沙成塔，如果每個家庭也分到2－3個口罩比有需要的人手中，<br />\n希望可以緩解現時資源緊絀的情況（大家都知道而家咁既情況責任誰屬）<br />\n100個人，每人有1個口罩，總比1個人有100個口罩的防疫效果好。<br />\n<br />\n個網主要功能就有三個<br />\n<br />\n一. 求助, 可以係地圖標示自己缺乏D乜野物資, 留底聯絡方法同一小段信息, 等其他人見到之後可以幫助到你<br />\n<br />\n二. 分享, 可以係地圖標示自己有咩物資多出黎可以分享, 留底聯絡方法同一小段信息, 等其他人聯絡你領取物資<br />\n<br />\n三. 售賣, 性質同分享類似, 只係變左係售賣, 係地圖既標示亦會唔同<br />\n<br />\n**以上所有標記都係可以自己刪除番既<br />\n****係個網度留底既聯絡方法係公開既, 所以唔好留底D太敏感既連絡方法啦<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n好老實講,我朋友真係唔太清楚呢個方法work唔work,<br />\n行唔行得通就真係睇下香港人願唔願意分享啦<br />\n有咩建議, bugs都可以係下面講番, <br />\n始終得我朋友一個人做可能會有少少bugs<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後, 兩盒,thx!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3edc1932fe3444dc195f6cca1b1ed6bf6bbe00","tid":1884323,"uid":55502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"係香港搞共享。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油。。。。。"},{"pid":"dd4b1360d5f66520fd5280fc89b0531babc42382","tid":1884323,"uid":253816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cc7f6b9b46ffdb5d2abef810399580efa497b3","tid":1884323,"uid":75592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d57e7db3425f2044c2c1c30e280f70f0d6eab37","tid":1884323,"uid":69134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"pish 試完可以反映下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5542c49ea95e30af47db2bd5e0bd6a5caa527b97","tid":1884323,"uid":69134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:59:02.000Z","msg":"臨訓前一推"},{"pid":"453ae1cbd6ede8366d3a0268c44351f2d2c26c81","tid":1884323,"uid":69134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35467a60a3ab872003ee6253b13bd6425beba2e","tid":1884323,"uid":12169,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"見有人賣$5個就唔想用個網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過多謝樓主先"},{"pid":"d4014f6fa2efc21d3fdbf9eb040a4d266dfc820d","tid":1884323,"uid":69134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a35467a60a3ab872003ee6253b13bd6425beba2e","tid":1884323,"uid":12169,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"見有人賣$5個就唔想用個網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過多謝樓主先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"如果可以加個filter, 可以filter走唔同既類別既marke